extendedInfo.description: Download the Jackson Hewitt Tax ServiceÂ® FREE app today and benefit from the expertise of an industry-leading provider of full service federal and state income tax preparation. Our exclusive Android Tax application makes it easy for you to: ESTIMATE YOUR REFUND - Quickly and easily estimate the amount of your 2013 tax refund. START YOUR TAX RETURN EARLY - Select a Jackson Hewitt office, then upload and share your tax documents.FIND US - Locate a Jackson Hewitt Office in your neighborhood using your phone's GPS technology. SCHEDULE AN APPOINTMENT - Instantly schedule a tax preparation appointment that's convenient for you. VIEW SPECIAL OFFERS - Access special discounts and offers valid on tax preparation services at a Jackson Hewitt location near you. CHECK THE STATUS OF YOUR TAX RETURN - Find out fast without having to call. Track the status of your tax return 24/7 on your phone. VIEW IN-OFFICE PRODUCTS - Easily find information on Jackson Hewitt's full line of in-office products and services.
